OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry but cloud will increase
OL,9,Flater to bring the odd spot of light
OL,10,Frain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,13,Fwith some hazy sunshine at times but
OL,14,Fthe odd light shower is possible. Warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCooler
OL,17,Fand cloudy over the weekend with a
OL,18,Fchance of showers, these most
OL,19,Fwidespread on Saturday. Rain at first
OL,20,Fon Monday then mainly dry.
